original_title: Josy Black: Spiel mit dem Feuer
overview: Josy Black, the hot fire of the Kenyan savannah burns in her. A woman like a volcano! If it extends its claws and loots you, bites you, it leaves the virus of craving black skin. Josy Black is the black big cat that you cannot escape!
title: Josy Black: Spiel mit dem Feuer
